sheet.description:
Expend a Wild Shape use to enter Guardian Form for 10 minutes, or until you are reduced to 0 hit points or end it with another bonus action. Gain the following:
Your AC is {{guardian form ac}};
As a bonus action you can crant yourself {{wisdom:modifier}} temporary hit points;
Your unarmed strike reach increases by 5 ft.;
You can use Wisdom instead of Strength for unarmed strike attack and damage rolls

Expend a Wild Shape use to enter Guardian Form for 1 hr., or until you are reduced to 0 hit points or end it with another bonus action. Gain the following:
You grow one size;
Your AC is {{guardian form ac}};
As a bonus action you can crant yourself {{wisdom:modifier}} temporary hit points;
Your unarmed strike reach increases by 5 ft.;
You can use Wisdom instead of Strength for unarmed strike attack and damage rolls;
You resist all bludgeoning, piercing, and slashing damage;
You can speak to plants in Druidic

Expend a Wild Shape use to take the form of a beast with CR 1 or less. You can expend a spell slot to empower it as follows:
It is covered in {{dragon gift color}} scales and has AC 13 + its dexterity modifier unless its natural AC was higher;
It resists {{dragon gift damage type}} damage;
it gains 5 times the expended slot's level in temporary hit points; you can use a bonus action to expend another spell slot and grant it 5 times that slot's level again

Expend a Wild Shape use to take the form of a beast with CR of 1/3 your Druid level ({{level:druid}}) or less. You can expend a spell slot to empower it as follows:
It is covered in {{dragon gift color}} scales and has AC 13 + its dexterity modifier unless its natural AC was higher;
It resists {{dragon gift damage type}} damage;
it gains 5 times the expended slot's level in temporary hit points; you can use a bonus action to expend another spell slot and grant it 5 times that slot's level again

Expend a Wild Shape use to take the form of a beast with CR of 1/3 your Druid level ({{level:druid}}) or less, or two uses for a beast with CR 5 or less. If the form is a dragon with a breath weapon, it can deal {{dragon gift damage type}} instead. You can expend a spell slot to empower it as follows:
It is covered in {{dragon gift color}} scales and has AC 13 + its dexterity modifier unless its natural AC was higher;
It resists {{dragon gift damage type}} damage;
it gains 5 times the expended slot's level in temporary hit points; you can use a bonus action to expend another spell slot and grant it 5 times that slot's level again

Expend a Wild Shape use to take the form of a beast with CR of 1/3 your Druid level ({{level:druid}}) or less, or two uses for a beast with CR 5 or less. If the form is a dragon with a breath weapon, it can deal {{dragon gift damage type}} instead. You can expend a spell slot to empower it as follows:
It is covered in {{dragon gift color}} scales and has AC 13 + its dexterity modifier unless its natural AC was higher;
It gains either 40 ft. flying or swimming speed
It resists {{dragon gift damage type}} damage;
it gains 5 times the expended slot's level in temporary hit points; you can use a bonus action to expend another spell slot and grant it 5 times that slot's level again
